 Jasmine Bloom, the CEO!"],[6389,6527,"I finally said it."],[6589,6781,"You will beg for mercy before she"],[6781,6952,"fires your father and destroys your"],[6952,7057,"pathetic little ass."]],"38":[[16,150,"Adam you should have told me earlier."],[150,375,"I find you weirdly intimidating."],[375,575,"And every time I have tried to tell you,"],[575,684,"you have cut me off."],[684,804,"You have brought this"],[804,1046,"upon yourself, Ricky. Rick."],[1284,1355,"Oh, God. I'm done."],[1355,1484,"I think I'm gonna throw up."],[1584,1747,"Oh, I just went toe to toe"],[1747,1822,"with Jasmine Bloom."],[1822,1931,"I gotta get out of California."],[1931,2202,"I have to get out of California, Dad. I ha-"],[2202,2473,"Miss Bloom, I am begging you."],[2473,2748,"I'm begging. I'm humbly begging you."],[2748,3048,"My dad has been loyal to you"],[3082,3265,"for years. For years."],[3265,3486,"Please don't punish him"],[3486,3557,"for something I did."],[3557,3820,"I will never do it again."],[3820,4049,"He's a perfect little soldier."],[4049,4225,"It's too late."],[4225,4596,"Abel. You’ve raised quite a boy."],[4596,4854,"How old are you now? 56?"],[4854,5084,"Maybe it's time for you to retire and"],[5084,5267,"focus on your family."],[5267,5355,"Oh my God."],[5509,5684,"We’re done."],[5684,5922,"We are just really, really, really done."],[5922,6151,"By no stretch of the imagination."],[6151,6431,"Is this man worthy of the CEO?"],[6431,6589,"It's not happening."],[6589,6823,"Listen, Miss Bloom, I am so sorry"],[6823,6969,"to be the one to tell you this, but"],[6969,7090,"you're being scammed."]],"39":[[20,241,"Yes, you must have been scammed."],[241,575,"There is no way that a jobless, penniless,"],[575,850,"crippled ex-vet could land the"],[850,980,"richest woman in America."],[1005,1105,"Yeah, I mean, I was with him for"],[1105,1263,"five years and every second of"],[1263,1363,"it was torture."],[1380,1447,"He's a bum."],[1476,1668,"Oh, so you're finally admitting"],[1735,1856,"that you were only with me because"],[1856,2014,"I funded your tuition back then?"],[2135,2310,"You've always known me to be resourceful."],[2310,2585,"You said Tobias is a no-good loser?"],[2857,3086,"You're all here, eating your oysters"],[3086,3265,"and drinking your fancy champagne"],[3265,3436,"without the slightest fear of"],[3436,3661,"getting bombed because of no-good"],[3661,3791,"men and women, just like"],[3791,4008,"him who protect our country."],[4346,4421,"You."],[4487,4562,"You."],[4688,4763,"You."],[4800,5059,"All of you would be dead if it"],[5059,5201,"wasn't for brave veterans like him."]],"40":[[112,408,"Tobias is not a no-good loser."],[408,558,"He's better, a hundred times,"],[558,663,"thousand times better than"],[663,800,"any of you will ever be."],[855,967,"How can you say that?"],[1021,1226,"I can't imagine what you see in him."],[1226,1351,"Like if it's the military thing,"],[1351,1526,"there are dozens others out there."],[1539,1718,"Not only did Tobias fend off"],[1718,1835,"the man I was supposed to marry,"],[1856,2156,"but he also got me a ten billion"],[2156,2452,"dollar deal with Stark Enterprises."],[2489,2610,"Stark Enterprises?"],[2660,2756,"That is the biggest"],[2756,2902,"conglomerate in the world."],[2936,3153,"And it's run by a five star general."],[3178,3440,"They call him CEO General."],[3461,3545,"That's impressive, right?"],[3578,3687,"Bloom Tech AI is"],[3687,3849,"nothing in comparison to them."],[3849,4037,"Tobias is the bravest man"],[4037,4141,"I have ever met."],[4200,4471,"And he is the man I am going to marry."],[4533,4679,"I was wondering what gave you the"],[4679,4879,"balls to crash my banquet and..."],[4967,5046,"That makes sense."],[5096,5242,"You got yourself a sugar mommy."],[5326,5388,"Pathetic."],[5463,5709,"Yeah. He has to have a woman to"],[5709,5826,"provide his handouts."],[5855,6064,"Jasmine is not my sugar mommy."],[6126,6172,"In fact,"],[6239,6360,"I outrank her."]],"41":[[41,166,"I outrank her."],[358,554,"Enough with the bluffing Tobias."],[575,725,"Nobody here believes you and"],[725,863,"you're not going to avoid being"],[863,1034,"called out publicly as a leech."],[1063,1167,"I know you."],[1167,1330,"No Daniella, you don't."],[1422,1572,"You dumped me before you got to"],[1572,1680,"know the real me."],[1680,1835,"But if you had just stuck around"],[1835,1993,"and been patient, you would have"],[1993,2135,"seen what I'm really worth."],[2189,2306,"But you lost out."],[2381,2610,"And thank you for throwing away"],[2610,2769,"your five-year relationship."],[2811,2894,"If you hadn't,"],[2894,3023,"I wouldn't have found him."],[3073,3332,"Oh, and by the way, Dr. Dunce,"],[3365,3478,"you're fired."],[3503,3553,"What?"],[3632,3728,"How can you?"],[3816,3962,"You made fun of my fiance."],[3995,4137,"And all the sisters and"],[4137,4312,"brothers on the battlefield."],[4325,4596,"No, no, no, no, no, no, no, no, no."],[4596,4763,"My seven-figure salary!"]],"42":[[0,200,"And the same goes for you two idiots."],[325,496,"You went against my future husband,"],[496,571,"which means you were"],[571,679,"going against me,"],[679,821,"and I, Jasmine Bloom,"],[821,1101,"will not stand for that. Understand?"],[1101,1201,"Sorry, ma’am."],[1347,1434,"Jasmine."],[1826,2035,"That was very cute."],[2035,2256,"But you don't need to protect me."],[2256,2402,"I will protect you."],[2402,2535,"You've already done enough"],[2535,2648,"in the military."],[2648,2865,"Jasmine, you're the best woman"],[2865,2998,"I've ever met."],[2998,3128,"You see, Daniella,"],[3128,3395,"this is what a good woman is like."],[3482,3603,"I must tell you my"],[3603,3803,"real identity soon, Jasmine."],[3803,3970,"Jasmine."],[3970,4254,"Who told you to fire Dr. Dunce?"]],"43":[[8,412,"Jasmine, who told you to fire Dr. Dunce?"],[517,604,"That's Mr. Bloom."],[604,721,"The patriarch of the Bloom family"],[721,909,"and the richest man on Wall Street."],[959,1009,"You didn't ask"],[1009,1138,"for Grandfather's permission."],[1292,1347,"Grandfather."],[1393,1534,"Know your place, Jasmine."],[1593,1822,"Joseph is the sole heir to Bloom Tech."],[1822,1985,"I only made you CEO so that you"],[1985,2081,"could take care of the company"],[2081,2173,"for your brother."],[2173,2277,"You can't just fire people"],[2277,2373,"without our approval."],[2385,2456,"Mr. Bloom, it's"],[2456,2565,"wonderful to have you here."],[2565,2656,"Please help us."],[2731,2836,"Grandpa, you promised that if"],[2836,2965,"I made Bloom Tech the largest AI"],[2965,3090,"company in America that you would-"],[3111,3236,"Don't call me Grandpa!"],[3574,3841,"I won't let anyone hurt my future wife."]],"44":[[104,250,"I promised I'd protect you."],[300,358,"Thank you."],[471,525,"Grandfather,"],[583,746,"these employees, they're revolting."],[767,988,"Shut up! Don't talk back to me."],[988,1151,"My dear sister, you're out of line."],[1247,1447,"Grandpa worked very hard"],[1447,1614,"to secure that marriage deal"],[1614,1818,"between you and David Lang."],[1818,2002,"And you eloped with"],[2002,2227,"this total piece of trash."],[2227,2377,"You only had one job."],[2435,2610,"Marry David Lang!"],[2610,2723,"No, I promise I would"],[2723,2857,"never give up my company"],[2857,3040,"and I will never marry David Lang."],[3040,3098,"Oh, don't worry"],[3098,3207,"about Bloom Tech anymore."],[3228,3294,"I've got it."],[3319,3374,"Enough, Jasmine."],[3449,3528,"I'm ordering you."],[3557,3749,"Apologize to Dr. Dunce."],[3820,3874,"Now!"],[3991,4129,"Yes, Daniella."],[4129,4258,"You're getting your job back."],[4304,4450,"But these people, they don't deserve-"],[4491,4625,"Abel's leadership is the reason"],[4625,4771,"Bloom Tech was so successful."],[4771,4854,"He's staying too."],[4892,5088,"Thank you, Mr. Bloom, thank you."],[5088,5288,"I built Bloom Tech from the ground up."],[5326,5484,"And Dr. Dunce, she's staying too."],[5484,5572,"With Stark Enterprises"],[5572,5793,"investing heavily in AI tech these days,"],[5793,5926,"Dr. Dunce's knowledge will be"],[5926,6043,"crucial to us securing"],[6043,6164,"a Stark Enterprise deal."],[6164,6227,"She's staying."],[6710,6861,"They still don't realize"],[6861,7019,"I’m the Toby Stark?"],[7061,7265,"Head of Stark Enterprises?"]],"45":[[58,87,"But-"],[87,183,"No buts!"],[216,329,"Why is it so hard"],[329,462,"for you to follow orders"],[462,571,"and marry David Lang?"],[596,784,"Grandpa, David Lang already publicly said"],[784,913,"that he won't bother me anymore."],[946,1088,"And it's all thanks to Tobias."],[1134,1338,"Why do you insist on me marrying him?"],[1363,1526,"The Langs are the biggest suppliers"],[1526,1714,"of steel to Stark Enterprises."],[1780,1918,"We'll be that much closer to a"],[1918,2022,"Stark investment deal."],[2089,2227,"We'll be American royalty."],[2394,2623,"But Grandpa, I'm your granddaughter."],[2623,2761,"What about my happiness?"],[2761,2915,"The family profits are far"],[2915,3003,"more important than your"],[3073,3207,"simple-minded happiness."],[3240,3340,"This is my life."],[3386,3516,"Why do I have to sacrifice my"],[3516,3728,"wishes for Joseph's success?"],[3799,3928,"You're being unfair, Grandpa."],[4004,4162,"I had no idea Jasmine's been"],[4162,4258,"under this much pressure."],[4304,4391,"I must help her."],[4491,4654,"Excuse me for interrupting."],[4671,4863,"But as far as I know, Jasmine is the"],[4863,5059,"brains that propped up Bloom Tech."],[5109,5226,"And you two meddling would"],[5226,5388,"only drive this precious company"],[5388,5484,"into the ground."],[5563,5634,"How dare"],[5689,5851,"a crippled man like you question me?"],[5885,6018,"You're not even a whole human being!"],[6085,6135,"Exactly."],[6239,6393,"You're just a piece of trash"],[6431,6627,"that Jasmine found on the street."],[6648,6723,"That's it, Jasmine."],[6794,6936,"Tomorrow, I'm taking you to the Langs."],[6936,7032,"And you're gonna beg for a"],[7032,7090,"marriage contract."],[7140,7344,"Mr. Bloom, have you gotten my"],[7344,7528,"permission before forcing my"],[7528,7761,"fiancée to marry another man?"]],"46":[[100,179,"Hilarious!"],[179,371,"This nobody's trying to tell me what to do!"],[475,579,"No Tobias,"],[579,725,"they're all too powerful, go!"],[800,971,"I'll face the consequences alone."],[984,1071,"Trust me."],[1297,1484,"I will always keep you safe."],[1797,1981,"I am Jasmine's future husband,"],[2043,2293,"and I won't let anyone hurt her."],[2360,2510,"And if anyone dares to,"],[2510,2756,"will have me to reckon with."],[2861,3019,"Pay him no mind, Mr. Bloom."],[3019,3207,"He is a little delusional"],[3207,3365,"from his time in the military."],[3365,3453,"Under the impression he's"],[3453,3536,"some sort of hero"],[3595,3691,"rather than the bum."],[3724,3924,"Yes, Mr. Bloom, this one-armed"],[3924,4087,"leech was messing with us earlier,"],[4087,4166,"because he had Lady Jasmine"],[4166,4245,"backing him up."],[4279,4421,"You gotta help us fight back."],[4429,4596,"You're getting too cocky, Jasmine."],[4800,4975,"Everyone in the tech industry calls your"],[4975,5171,"granddaughter Lady Jasmine"],[5201,5309,"out of respect for"],[5309,5401,"what she's accomplished."],[5426,5559,"Punk, you don't have any real life"],[5559,5672,"experience, so I'll give you"],[5672,5747,"some advice."],[5747,5901,"Stay away from my family business."],[5926,6051,"A nothing like you isn't fit to"],[6051,6106,"marry a Bloom."],[6122,6214,"I don't care."],[6289,6435,"I've made up my mind."],[6502,6631,"I'm going to marry Tobias."],[6735,6902,"Disobey me again and I'll fire you too."],[6948,7102,"You don't have to worry, Jasmine."],[7198,7257,"I can give her"],[7257,7407,"whatever David Lang can,"],[7440,7570,"and a hundred times over."]],"47":[[237,400,"Did this crippled military idiot"],[400,492,"just say that?"],[579,709,"He must have been bonked on the head"],[709,825,"too many times or something."],[896,1084,"He's not even in the military anymore."],[1142,1351,"They let him go when he lost his arm."],[1351,1518,"Yeah, all he has left is that"],[1518,1655,"piece of scrap metal."],[1676,1856,"Lowest of the bottom feeders."],[1893,2006,"How did we put it earlier?"],[2035,2302,"Oh, yes, not even a full man."],[2373,2485,"Know your place."],[2535,2660,"Or I'll beat it into your head"],[2660,2823,"with your silly little robot arm."],[2898,3115,"Tobias, I need to be honest with you."],[3178,3336,"I asked you to marry me so I"],[3336,3549,"would have a way out of this family, but"],[3549,3682,"I can see now that there's no way that'll"],[3682,3799,"happen without hurting you."],[3874,4045,"I will marry David Lang."],[4091,4204,"Please, just go."]],"48":[[41,183,"Jasmine, do you think I'm a"],[183,308,"no-good loser too?"],[350,417,"No."],[467,588,"You're an American hero."],[588,709,"I, I just don't want you to get caught"],[709,829,"up in my family drama."],[880,946,"Trust me,"],[996,1105,"I will protect you."],[1151,1338,"Since you're not even her real fiancé,"],[1409,1518,"you better get out of here"],[1559,1710,"before I kick your ass."],[1976,2039,"You're right."],[2131,2268,"We weren't really engaged."],[2302,2394,"But we are now."],[3995,4074,"Jasmine Bloom..."],[4250,4387,"will you marry me?"]],"49":[[33,200,"Damn it, Tobias, what are you doing?"],[221,287,"Get up!"],[350,450,"This one-armed G.I. Joe"],[450,583,"doesn't know his place."],[592,800,"Mr. Bloom already arranged"],[800,938,"Jasmine's marriage with the Langs."],[959,1063,"They and Stark Enterprises"],[1063,1222,"have been lifelong partners."],[1222,1455,"Jasmine Bloom, you are an idiot"],[1455,1609,"if you choose this nobody"],[1609,1697,"over David Lang."],[1785,1847,"Exactly."],[1872,2039,"Tobias is just blind."],[2131,2377,"Apparently, he needs his sugar mama,"],[2377,2569,"and all of her sweetness."],[2619,2736,"Tobias, David Lang has"],[2736,2927,"Stark Enterprises on his side."],[2927,3082,"That may make you in danger."],[3082,3178,"Are you sure about this?"],[3207,3386,"Didn't you propose to me earlier?"],[3453,3570,"I'm returning the favor."],[3570,3707,"You don't seem like the kind of woman"],[3707,3891,"that would be scared of the Starks."],[3983,4037,"I'm not."],[4104,4216,"But are you?"],[4270,4387,"Oh, I'm not scared at all."],[4429,4500,"Whatever happens,"],[4562,4654,"I've got your back."]],"50":[[266,337,"Jasmine!"],[337,517,"You say yes to this good-for-nothing,"],[542,684,"I will remove you as CEO!"],[684,809,"Everyone else in the world wants"],[809,971,"me to marry someone I despise."],[1063,1242,"Only Tobias is on my side."],[1338,1422,"I want him."],[1505,1655,"He's my ride or die."],[1760,1805,"Yes."],[1893,2043,"Yes, I'll marry you."],[2410,2502,"From now on,"],[2544,2665,"it's us against the world."],[4412,4500,"Yeah!"],[5096,5338,"Jasmine Bloom is my fiancée."],[5401,5543,"Who's got a problem with that?"],[5563,5655,"Jasmine Bloom,"],[5689,5860,"how dare you accept his proposal."],[5885,5972,"I hereby announce,"],[5993,6260,"Jasmine is no longer CEO of Bloom Tech."],[6414,6464,"You hear that?"],[6544,6702,"I can't give you anything now."],[6744,6815,"I've never needed"],[6815,6911,"you to give me anything."],[6994,7065,"I'm giving you"],[7065,7253,"everything, remember?"],[7286,7499,"I got you that Stark Enterprises funding."]],"51":[[29,79,"What?"],[187,342,"Stark Enterprises' investment is"],[342,508,"like a godsend in this industry."],[533,692,"It's easy as pie when"],[692,984,"I’m the CEO General of Stark Enterprises."],[1038,1234,"Dude, you're crazy."],[1234,1368,"I got that funding from"],[1368,1468,"Stark Enterprises."],[1468,1710,"You're nothing but a jobless, armless vet."],[1726,1885,"What pull could you possibly have?"],[1914,2152,"You got the Stark Enterprises funding?"],[2168,2335,"Yes. Me."],[2360,2510,"Stark Enterprises' new"],[2510,2706,"regional manager, Ken Baker, has a"],[2706,2986,"big drone project with the Pentagon."],[2986,3224,"I reached out to him about installing our"],[3224,3428,"model into the drones, and he"],[3428,3549,"helped me get that"],[3549,3682,"Ten billion dollar deal."],[3712,3824,"Ken Baker, you say?"],[3824,4079,"He's really close with the military generals."],[4079,4170,"It's how he gets all of his"],[4170,4275,"government contracts."],[4287,4508,"Oh, right. It's Stark Enterprises' new"],[4508,4667,"CEO's first day tomorrow."],[4667,4767,"They're having a banquet."],[4788,4975,"He means my banquet."],[5017,5138,"Ken invited me too."],[5209,5442,"He's introducing me to his new boss."],[5442,5576,"And once I become friends"],[5663,5814,"with the Stark CEO,"],[5814,5980,"I will raise our family's business"],[5980,6172,"value by a hundred times."],[6277,6410,"Why, congrats!"],[6510,6614,"I'll see you there, then."]],"52":[[120,275,"Joseph is soaring higher than you"],[275,479,"could imagine while you maintain your"],[479,621,"residency at the bottom."],[621,721,"Atta boy, Joseph."],[759,875,"Lock down that Stark"],[875,975,"business partnership."],[992,1105,"We'll be American royalty!"],[1105,1322,"Oh yes, yes. God bless America"],[1322,1501,"and God bless the Blooms."],[1593,1864,"Daniella, if you get with the CEO"],[1864,2039,"of Stark Enterprises,"],[2039,2177,"you will be the queen."],[2202,2289,"Of course."],[2293,2394,"I know what to do, Mom."],[2431,2669,"Mr. Bloom, you do know that"],[2669,2927,"Daniella is the head of R&D."],[2965,3119,"Perhaps you should invite her"],[3119,3190,"to the banquet."],[3211,3361,"Why yes, of course."],[3390,3503,"Anything to impress the"],[3503,3670,"almighty Stark CEO."],[3703,3912,"Ken has allowed me to bring all"],[3912,4099,"of Bloom Tech, if I so please."],[4250,4316,"Anyone but"],[4383,4450,"these two."],[4558,4779,"And as soon as I gain the CEO's favor,"],[4863,4963,"I'll step on you two"],[5100,5234,"like cockroaches."],[5234,5367,"Oh, I'll look forward to it."],[5430,5668,"We'll see who steps on who."]],"53":[[70,158,"Let's go, my lady."],[321,387,"Bye."],[809,1005,"249 years ago,"],[1030,1130,"America was born,"],[1130,1288,"and now, Jasmine Bloom"],[1338,1413,"has a new start."],[1488,1651,"Don't let the little things bother you."],[1755,1851,"It's going to be okay."],[1960,2227,"But, if Joseph becomes business"],[2227,2419,"partners with the new Stark CEO,"],[2489,2602,"my new beginning will be over"],[2602,2740,"before it even starts."],[3015,3073,"Jasmine."],[3161,3236,"Trust me."],[3253,3440,"Tomorrow's gonna be a great day for us."],[3561,3632,"Tobias, I'm sorry."],[3632,3849,"I wanted to help you get revenge on your"],[3849,4079,"ex-girlfriend, but I can't even"],[4079,4200,"protect myself now."],[4241,4404,"Jasmine, you're my life partner."],[4483,4554,"Whatever happens,"],[4554,4667,"I'm gonna be by your side."],[4667,4733,"Don't let the warriors"],[4733,4871,"cloud the sky in front of you."],[4904,4959,"Tobias,"],[5050,5246,"meeting you has been the"],[5246,5426,"best thing that's ever happened to me."],[5488,5697,"I used to be so on guard because"],[5697,5780,"of my family."],[5901,5947,"I've never felt"],[5947,6122,"so at ease with someone before."]],"54":[[3169,3219,"Mr. Stark."],[3311,3365,"Sir,"],[3415,3553,"your first day banquet is set."],[3586,3707,"We sent Ms. Jasmine Bloom"],[3707,3795,"an invitation."],[3832,3912,"Good work, Max."],[4058,4141,"Today's the day"],[4141,4337,"I'll be showing my true identity,"],[4391,4600,"and also introducing the"],[4600,4742,"shiniest star to the world,"],[4792,4900,"my Mrs. Stark."]],"55":[[308,709,"Oh my word, this place is stunning."],[750,896,"Must have cost a fortune."],[925,1026,"The most upscale"],[1026,1242,"high-tech place in all of America."],[1351,1443,"Designed and owned by"],[1443,1601,"the CEO Stark himself."],[1601,1693,"God, what a legend."],[1714,1876,"I know, I cannot wait to meet the"],[1876,1976,"new CEO in person."],[2031,2152,"CEO General, that is."],[2152,2235,"You know they call him that"],[2235,2423,"because he's actually a five-star general?"],[2494,2640,"Daniella, this new CEO"],[2640,2865,"is the crème de la crème."],[2936,3053,"You must land him."],[3053,3240,"Oh, I know. Lock him down."],[3361,3524,"We'll never work for anything ever again."],[3524,3707,"Did you guys also know"],[3707,3845,"that the four star general,"],[3845,4016,"Tom Evans, is going to be here today?"],[4045,4141,"Fantastic!"],[4258,4362,"We're gonna meet so"],[4362,4479,"many important people."],[4554,4671,"Oh my God."],[4938,5050,"Is that Tobias?"],[5113,5192,"What is he doing at"],[5192,5288,"the General's banquet?"]],"56":[[350,412,"Well,"],[412,596,"will you look what the cat dragged in?"],[654,838,"And you're in your big boy pants."],[875,1013,"Rent the suit?"],[1013,1205,"It looks cheap."],[1305,1430,"I mean, I prefer to own,"],[1430,1697,"but I have to say I am missing your"],[1697,1876,"dusty old uniform."],[1876,1989,"What are you doing here?"],[1989,2068,"This is the Stark"],[2068,2298,"CEO's first day banquet."],[2298,2502,"I didn't think they invited bums."],[2523,2623,"Yes, Tobias,"],[2623,2806,"it's really best if you leave now."],[2806,2944,"Even Jasmine Bloom can't protect"],[2944,3144,"you from a pissed off CEO."],[3144,3236,"This is the CEO"],[3236,3436,"General's first day banquet."],[3436,3570,"Why can't I be here?"],[3728,3841,"I am him!"]],"57":[[0,225,"Well for starters, you're a leech."],[225,371,"If you thought the Bloom Banker was"],[371,600,"impressive with the top 1%,"],[600,754,"look around you."],[754,921,"This is the top 1/100th of a percent"],[921,1046,"and I recommend"],[1046,1238,"disappearing before they see you."],[1238,1426,"So what? I'm not leeching on you."],[1451,1589,"But don't forget,"],[1589,1722,"I paid for your schooling."],[1751,1872,"And I haven't even gotten"],[1872,1951,"a thank you."],[2018,2156,"Well, don't hold your breath."],[2156,2256,"I'll be sure to pay you back"],[2256,2377,"with my first paycheck."],[2377,2481,"Oh, so you're the one"],[2481,2656,"relying on handouts then?"],[2761,2873,"Whatever you say."],[2927,3148,"You see, the Stark CEO,"],[3148,3353,"he's very much into smart girls."],[3353,3511,"Meaning I'm just his type."],[3511,3641,"That's right."],[3641,3724,"You're looking at"],[3724,3962,"the next Mrs. CEO."],[4033,4145,"My Daniella."],[4158,4245,"It's me."],[4245,4416,"That confident smile."],[4416,4600,"Let me burn that into my memory"],[4600,4813,"before it's wiped off your face."],[4942,5063,"Get your head out of your ass,"],[5063,5171,"Tobias."],[5217,5392,"You're Jasmine Bloom's problem now."],[5426,5509,"And no other woman"],[5509,5626,"could compete with me."],[5643,5726,"You know, Daniella,"],[5726,5843,"your mom was right."],[5880,5980,"You could have been the CEO"],[5980,6143,"General's wife, but you lost that"],[6143,6260,"chance when you dumped me."],[6435,6652,"That ship has sailed."],[6652,6881,"What are you talking about?"],[6881,6998,"Am I not clear?"],[7048,7361,"I am the new Stark CEO."]],"58":[[312,492,"Okay, GI Joe."],[492,571,"Hey, you should really stop"],[571,729,"popping those pills."],[784,971,"Security, get him out of here."],[1001,1146,"Don't you dare touch him."],[1655,1843,"He is my husband, and none of you"],[1843,2027,"here are qualified to kick him out."],[2077,2214,"Jasmine, do you still think"],[2214,2314,"Bloom Tech AI"],[2314,2439,"is under your control?"],[2439,2502,"How did you two"],[2502,2619,"even get in here?"],[2619,2736,"Where are your invitations?"],[2736,2815,"She doesn't need an invitation"],[2815,2940,"when she's with me."],[3011,3190,"We took the VIP entrance."],[3365,3449,"And how would they have gotten to"],[3449,3582,"the VIP entrance if you told me"],[3582,3716,"that was for upper management only?"],[3741,3820,"I don't know, but..."],[3945,4149,"It's... bribe security or something."],[4216,4362,"They'll be thrown out in a second, okay?"],[4362,4587,"This is the Stark CEO's banquet."],[4696,4842,"You're not invited, Jasmine."],[4921,5180,"And you... the garbage is outside."],[5238,5326,"Now get out of here."]],"59":[[0,271,"Stark Enterprises did invite me,"],[287,579,"and my fiancé Tobias is my plus one."],[579,738,"Do you have a problem with that?"],[759,992,"Look, Jasmine, I know you want to"],[992,1209,"save your spot at Bloom Tech,"],[1209,1539,"but you won't meet the CEO like this."],[1576,1655,"Without Ken,"],[1655,1860,"you won't even see his shoelace."],[1889,1985,"That's not for you"],[1985,2214,"nor Ken to decide."],[2239,2377,"Jas,"],[2377,2498,"aren't you ashamed of bringing"],[2498,2694,"your unemployed loser hubby here?"],[2694,2919,"Show some respect, Joseph."],[2919,3040,"That's okay, honey."],[3040,3265,"Let these lowlives think whatever."],[3315,3478,"Yeah, that's right."],[3478,3586,"Get out of here."],[3645,3724,"He's so poor,"],[3724,3820,"he probably came here"],[3820,3974,"trying to bum a free meal."],[4279,4325,"Man,"],[4325,4491,"you two unemployed losers just"],[4491,4633,"flock together, don't you?"],[4650,4813,"I don't care what you say to me,"],[4813,4971,"but don't be rude to my wife."],[5163,5313,"No one here will protect you."]],"60":[[25,112,"Oh?"],[237,312,"And"],[312,563,"who’s gonna protect you, Jasmine?"],[604,725,"Hey, everybody!"],[763,846,"Come on,"],[896,1026,"get a look at this pair."],[1138,1313,"My dumb sister"],[1313,1614,"shamed my elite Wall Street family"],[1614,1751,"by getting engaged"],[1751,2072,"to this unemployed loser vet."],[2110,2181,"Maybe"],[2181,2356,"they should be thrown out together."],[2435,2615,"Jasmine, didn't I tell you"],[2615,2769,"not to show your face here again?"],[2769,2969,"Grandfather, I've made up my mind."],[2969,3086,"I want to be with Tobias"],[3086,3203,"for the rest of my life."],[3282,3495,"If you and this welfare leech,"],[3536,3707,"piss off Stark Enterprises,"],[3707,3866,"our whole family can go under."],[3866,4070,"Don't worry, old man, Jasmine"],[4070,4225,"will never piss off the Stark CEO."],[4270,4471,"And as for you, arrogant snobs,"],[4471,4650,"I don't think the CEO General"],[4650,4763,"will like you at all."],[4833,4992,"Jasmine, if you insist"],[4992,5217,"on marrying this loudmouth,"],[5217,5388,"unemployed nobody,"],[5401,5522,"you leave me no choice."],[5572,5764,"I hereby announce,"],[5764,5985,"Jasmine Bloom is no longer a Bloom."],[6031,6202,"She's been disowned."]],"61":[[25,100,"Grandfather!"],[200,379,"Take your crippled vet husband and"],[379,538,"leave. The Bloom family has severed"],[538,709,"all ties with you, Jasmine."],[721,880,"But we're family, Grandpa."],[900,1055,"I'll say this one more time."],[1096,1251,"You are no longer a member"],[1251,1363,"of this Bloom family."],[1363,1501,"But I've done so much"],[1522,1609,"for you and Joseph."],[1609,1839,"I've dedicated my life to Bloom Tech."],[1939,2014,"Quiet!"],[2360,2560,"I've told you this before."],[2560,2727,"You hurt my wife."],[2727,2865,"You've got me to reckon with."],[3032,3415,"You? Who are you but a bum vet?"],[3415,3541,"Do you know where we are?"],[3582,3820,"Yes, this is my property"],[3820,4029,"because I am the CEO General"],[4029,4179,"of Stark Enterprises."],[4179,4396,"This is Stark Enterprises."],[4433,4579,"The Stark CEO wouldn't tolerate"],[4579,4708,"filth like you on his property."],[4708,4879,"The only filth here is you."],[4896,5055,"Enough! I won't allow you two to"],[5055,5192,"embarrass us any further."],[5221,5413,"Security! Throw them out!"],[7394,7490,"How the"],[7490,7695,"hell did he do that?"],[7695,7803,"Oh, shit."]],"62":[[62,100,"Oh shit."],[229,404,"I heard the Stark CEO also has a"],[404,513,"mechanical right arm that can knock"],[513,696,"like 20 people away."],[763,909,"Oh god, could it really be him?"],[909,1172,"No, no, no, no, no. The CEO"],[1172,1343,"General. He's a five star General."],[1405,1459,"Tobias is nothing"],[1459,1547,"but a lowly ex-marine."],[1647,1843,"Don't psych yourself out. Tobias is"],[1843,1981,"just a brute from the military."],[2043,2239,"I only act in self defense. Unlike"],[2239,2402,